snippet.title: King of Thieves - Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
King of Thieves - new multiplayer game from Zeptolab - is available today on iOS and Android. Download here:

Apple App Store: http://zep.tl/youtube/kt/ios
Google Play: http://zep.tl/tube/kt/android
Amazon: http://zep.tl/tube/kt/amazon

King of Thieves, a competitive multiplayer game, combines the high-quality art and animations ZeptoLab is known for with platforming and tower defense elements to create an all-new, challenging gameplay experience.

More info - http://www.kingofthieves.com
